This paper deals with conversational QA and neural models, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the issue of models exploiting superficial patterns in data, which is a problem that falls under the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
